📖 Surah Al-Kausar

🌟 Taruf:

➡️Surah Al-Kausar Qur’an ki sabse chhoti surah hai (sirf 3 ayat).
➡️Ye surah tasalli aur himmat ke taur par Nabi Muhammad ﷺ ko di gayi thi.
➡️Jab Nabi ﷺ ke betay (Qasim aur Abdullah) wafat hue to Quraysh ke mushrikeen ne kaha:
     “Muhammad ab abtar (nasl kat gayi) ho gaye hain.”
➡️Is par Allah ne jawab diya ke asli “abtar” to Nabi ﷺ ke dushman honge, magar Nabi ﷺ ka zikr hamesha qayam rahega.

_____________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

📝 Word-by-Word  with Tafsir

                                                                     بِسْمِ اللّٰہِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِیْمِ
                                                                  Bismillaahir-Rahmaanir-Raheem
                                       "Allah ke Naam se shuru karta hoon, jo bohot Meherbaan aur Nihayat Reham Karne Wala hai." 


🌸Ayat 1: إِنَّا أَعْطَيْنَاكَ الْكَوْثَرَ
Transliteration: Inna a‘tainaka al-Kauthar
Roman Urdu Meaning: “Beshak humne aapko Kausar ata ki.”

🔹 Kausar ka matlab:

➡️“Kausar” ek bohot badi ni’mat aur khair hai jo Allah ne Nabi ﷺ ko di.
➡️Riwayaton mein Kausar ka zikr Jannat ki ek nahr (nadi) ke taur par aaya hai:
  Uska paani doodh se safed, shahad se meetha, aur misk se bhi zyada khushbu daar hai.
  Uske kinare moti aur yaqoot (jewels) ke bane hain.
➡️Iske ilawa, “Kausar” se murad:
  Nabuwat
  Qur’an
  Sahaba aur ummat
  Nabi ﷺ ka naam qayamat tak zinda rehna

_____________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

🌸Ayat 2: فَصَلِّ لِرَبِّكَ وَانْحَرْ
Transliteration: Fasalli li rabbika wanhar
Roman Urdu Meaning: “To apne Rab ke liye namaz padho aur qurbani karo.”

🔹 Tafsir:

➡️Allah ki badi ni’mat ka shukr sirf ibadat se ada hota hai.
➡️Yahan do ahem ibadatein zikr hui:
  Namaz (Salat) – Rabb ki bando ko yaad karne ki sabse bari ibadat.
  Qurbani (Nahr) – Hajj aur Eid al-Adha ke waqt Allah ke liye jaanwar qurbaan karna.
➡️Is ayat mein ek pegham hai ke ibadat aur qurbani sirf Allah ke liye hai, kisi aur ke liye nahi (shirk se inkaar).

_____________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

🌸Ayat 3: إِنَّ شَانِئَكَ هُوَ الْأَبْتَرُ
Transliteration: Inna shani’aka huwal abtar
Roman Urdu Meaning: “Beshak aapka dushman hi abtar (nasl katne wala) hai.”

🔹 Tafsir:

➡️Mushrikeen kehte the ke Nabi ﷺ ke betay wafat ho gaye, ab aapka naam mit jaayega.
➡️Allah ne unke daaway ka ulta jawab diya:
   Nabi ﷺ ka zikr qayamat tak hamesha zinda rahega.
   Har din azaan mein, namaz mein, darood mein Nabi ﷺ ka naam liya jaata hai.
➡️Lekin Nabi ﷺ ke dushman (Abu Jahl, Abu Lahab, etc.) ka naam aur izzat mit gayi.
➡️“Abtar” ka matlab hai jo kata hua ho, jiska aage silsila na chale.

_____________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

🌹 Ahmiyat aur Lessons:

➡️Allah ne Nabi ﷺ ko be-hisab ni’matein di hain.
➡️Shukr ada karne ka asal tareeqa: Namaz aur Qurbani sirf Allah ke liye.
➡️Nabi ﷺ ka zikr aur shan hamesha zinda rahegi.
➡️Allah ke dushman hamesha ruswayi aur zaleel honge.
➡️Musalman ko bhi apne Rabb ki ni’maton par shukr ada karna chahiye.

_____________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

✨ Practical Reflection for Us :-

➡️Humein hamesha Allah ki ni’maton ka shukr ada karna chahiye.
➡️Shukr ka tareeqa sirf zabaan se nahi, balki ibadat aur amal se hai.
➡️Sirf Allah ke liye ibadat aur qurbani karna chahiye.
➡️Nabi ﷺ ki sunnat aur zikr ko zinda rakhna har Musalman ka farz hai.
➡️Allah ke dushman kitni bhi taaqat rakhte ho, akhir mein unka naam mit jaata hai.

_____________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

🌸 Dua from Surah Al-Kausar Reflection

🤲 Ya Allah! Humein apni di hui ni’maton ka shukr ada karne ki tofeeq ata farma.
🤲 Humein un logon mein shamil farma jo sirf Tere liye namaz aur qurbani karte hain.
🤲 Ya Rabb! Nabi ﷺ ke zikr aur sunnat ko hamesha zinda rakhne ki tofeeq ata farma.
🤲 Aur humein un dushmanon ki tarah na bana jo ruswayi aur zillat mein doob gaye.
🤲 “Ya Allah! Humein un logon mein shamil farma jinka zikr aur amal qayamat tak roshan rahe.” 

